snippet.title: Diana Pretends to be a Singer with a new Doll Candy Town
snippet.description:
Parents, you can find Love, Diana at Big W in Australia: https://bit.ly/3goBZkH
Diana has a new doll - Love Diana Candy Town. Diana pretends to be a singer and sings a Candy Town song along with a new doll!
Thanks for watching!
Subscribe to Kids Diana Show - http://bit.ly/2k7NrSx
